pool.Title: Liquidity provider rewards
pool.SubTitle: Liquidity providers earn a 0.3% fee on all trades proportional to their share of the pool. Fees are added to the pool, accrue in real time and can be claimed by withdrawing your liquidity.

MigrateV1Exchange.CorrectPrice: It's best to deposit liquidity into Waltonchain-swap V2 at a price you believe is correct. If the V2 price seems incorrect, you can either make a swap to move the price or wait for someone else to do so.
MigrateV1Exchange.MigratedPool: You are the first liquidity provider for this pair on Waltonchain-swap V2. Your liquidity will be migrated at the current V1 price. Your transaction cost also includes the gas to create the pool.
MigrateV1Exchange.MigrateV2: Migrate your liquidity tokens from Waltonchain-swap V1 to Waltonchain-swap V2.
MigrateV1Exchange.HoodMigrated: Because Waltonchain-swap V2 uses WETH under the hood, your Waltonchain-swap V1 WETH/ETH liquidity cannot be migrated. You may want to remove your liquidity instead.
